Items.text: Well son, your first week has been quite eventful!
Items.name: Dad

Items.text: Seems like the superhero thing comes naturally for ya, haha!
Items.name: Dad

Items.text: Honey, you've had a big day and I'm sure you're tired.
Items.name: Mom

Items.text: We'll let you get off to finishing any homework and getting to rest.
Items.name: Mom

Items.text: I'm proud of you son. Good luck at your dodgeball tryouts tomorrow.
Items.name: Dad
